I am excited to announce that I will be starting as a full time Systems Engineer I with Interlaced.io in San Diego this coming week. I am very grateful for the opportunity to work with this amazing company. I am eager to learn and grow in this role and cannot wait to see where this new chapter takes me. I want to thank Interlaced for giving me this opportunity and want to thank my friends and family for supporting me along the way!
